---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Srenix &mdash; Terms"
  description="Terms of use for srenix.ai: as-is content, Apache-2.0 OSS code, trademarks, acceptable use."
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="Legal" title="Terms of use" />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
      <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-500">Last updated: 2026-06-11</p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">1. Acceptance</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          By using srenix.ai (the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;), operated by
          Srenix, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree,
          do not use the Site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">2. Content is provided as-is</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          The Site's content is provided for general information about the
          Agentic SRE (Srenix) project, &ldquo;as is&rdquo; and
          without warranty of any kind, express or implied — including
          warranties of accuracy, merchantability, fitness for a particular
          purpose, or non-infringement. Product capabilities, roadmaps, and
          version details described here may change without notice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">3. Open-source software</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          The Srenix open-source code is licensed under the
          <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="https://github.com/srenix-ai/agentic-sre/blob/main/LICENSE">Apache License 2.0</a>;
          your use of that code is governed solely by that license, not these
          terms. Paid Srenix tiers are governed by a separate commercial
          agreement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">4. Trademarks</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          &ldquo;Srenix&rdquo; and &ldquo;Agentic SRE&rdquo; are names and
          marks of Srenix. The Apache-2.0 license for the code does not
          grant trademark rights. Third-party names on the Site (Kubernetes,
          AWS, GCP, Azure, Slack, and others) are trademarks of their
          respective owners and are used for identification only.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">5. Acceptable use</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Do not use the Site to attempt unauthorized access to our systems,
          disrupt the Site's operation, or misrepresent affiliation with
          Srenix. Security findings should go to
          <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="mailto:security@srenix.ai">security@srenix.ai</a>
          (see <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="/security/">Security</a>), not exploited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Srenix is not
          liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
          arising from your use of the Site or reliance on its content.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">7. Governing law</h2>
        <!-- TODO(owner): confirm jurisdiction before publishing externally-marketed paid tiers -->
        <p class="mt-2">
          These terms are governed by the laws of India, without regard to
          conflict-of-law rules.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Questions about these terms:
          <a class="font-medium text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-700 dark:text-accent-400" href="mailto:hello@srenix.ai">hello@srenix.ai</a>.
